+# SoftChat (Expo + Firebase)
+
+A modern messaging app scaffold with:
+- Username login
+- Real-time chat state hooks (ready to wire Firestore listeners)
+- Online indicators
+- Read receipts
+- Voice note entry point
+- Push notification registration
+- Premium page ($1/month) + US SMS add-on architecture note (Twilio)
+
+## Run
+
+1. Install dependencies:
+   ```bash
+   npm install
+   ```
+2. Set Firebase env vars in `.env`:
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID
+   - EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID
+3. Start:
+   ```bash
+   npm run start
+   ```
+
+## Structure
+- `src/pages`: Splash, Auth, Chats, Discover, Chat Room, Profile, Settings, Premium
+- `src/services/firebase.ts`: Firebase bootstrap
+- `src/services/notifications.ts`: Expo push registration
+
+## Premium SMS
+Use Firebase Cloud Functions + Twilio for provisioning and routing through a real US number.
